---
title: Cal Smart Tomato Poached Salmon with Cannellini Beans and Olives
description: This dinner will wow you with its simplicity and robust flavours. Creamy cannellini beans add a wonderful texture to tender salmon. A sprinkling of feta makes this whole dish come alive!

